<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Blisser Privacy Policy</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to Blisser Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Welcome to Blisser, your trusted online grocery app powered by BlissNova PVT LTD.! At Blisser, we are committed to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and protection of your data. We do not collect sensitive data of users and do not share any information with third parties. Please read this policy carefully to understand how we handle your information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect:</h2>
    <p>Blisser does not collect sensitive data such as race, ethnicity, religion, political beliefs, sexual orientation, or health information. We believe in respecting your privacy and limiting the data we collect to the absolute essentials for our service.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect:</h2>
    <p>
        <b>a. Personal Information:</b> We collect only the minimal personal information required for registration and order processing. This includes your name, contact information (email and phone number), and delivery address.
        <br>
        <b>b. Order Information:</b> We collect the details of your grocery orders, including the items you purchase, delivery preferences, and payment information (if you choose to save it for future use). Your payment details are securely processed by trusted payment service providers.
        <br>
        <b>c. Usage Information:</b> We may collect non-sensitive data related to your interactions with our app, such as the pages visited, items viewed, and time spent on the app. This information helps us improve our services.
    </p>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information:</h2>
    <p>
        <b>a. Order Processing:</b> Your personal information is used to facilitate your orders and ensure timely delivery of groceries.
        <br>
        <b>b. Communication:</b> We may use your contact information to provide you with order updates, confirmations, and essential service-related communications.
        <br>
        <b>c. App Improvement:</b> Non-sensitive usage data is used to enhance your experience by optimizing our app and services.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Sharing Information:</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal or sensitive data with third parties for any purpose, except when required by law.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security:</h2>
    <p>Blisser employs industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Choices:</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You can also opt-out of receiving non-essential communications.</p>

    <h2>7. Children's Privacy:</h2>
    <p>Blisser is intended for users aged 18 and above. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13 years of age.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to this Policy:</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. You will be notified of any significant changes, and the updated policy will be made available on our app.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us:</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:bliss@blisser.online">bliss@blisser.online</a>.</p>

    <p>By using Blisser, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Your trust is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your privacy while providing you with a convenient online grocery shopping experience.</p>
</body>
</html>
